items.title: International Business Machines (NYSE:IBM) Partners With Deca For Advanced Chiplet Packaging Expansion
items.description: International Business Machines (NYSE:IBM) experienced a price move of approximately 12% over the last month, coinciding with several significant corporate developments, including a newly announced partnership with Deca Technologies to integrate advanced packaging technology at IBM's facility in Bromont, Quebec.
